data.text:
New! A previously unreleased 4 song set from a small gathering of friends in early 1980, before the band had even recorded their first LP AND featuring three songs NEVER before released or heard by the public (unless you were at one of those earliest performances). A stellar set discovered at the end of an old Jabbers mix-tape, lost & forgotten since 1980! Comes with a limited edition 7x7 2-sided color insert.

GLORIA

DEATHCHILD

UNPREDICTABLE

CALIFORNIA SUN
